  <summary date="2021-04-09T15:38:52Z" status="Reported to Senate">Land and Water Conservation Fund Permanent Funding Act

This bill makes permanent, beginning in FY2020,&#160;funding for the Land and Water Conservation Fund (LWCF).

The President shall annually submit to Congress specified details regarding the allocation of the full amounts of funds made available to the LWCF. Congress may provide for alternate allocations using specified procedures.</summary>
